# Deploy

Push `main` → GitHub Actions v7. Skill: `deploy`.

Port/runtime → **`12-production-port.mdc`** (do not duplicate port rules here).

| Step | Command |
|------|---------|
| Stop before build | `pm2 stop darulquran-next` |
| Install & build | `npm ci` → `npm run build` |
| Start | `pm2 start ecosystem.config.cjs --update-env` |
| Health | curl `LOCAL_URL` from `deploy/runtime.cjs` + sample chunk |

Critical: stop PM2 **before** touching `.next`. Verify chunk URL after restart. Apache serves `/_next/static/`.

Never `rm -rf .next` while PM2 is serving.

## CI (GitHub Actions)

On PR + `main`: `lint` → `check:urdu` → `test` → `npm audit --audit-level=high` → `build`

Dependabot: `.github/dependabot.yml` (weekly)

## Production env checklist

After deploy, verify VPS `.env` includes (see `.env.example`):

- `REVALIDATE_SECRET` + Sanity webhook (`setup-revalidation` skill)
- `RESEND_API_KEY` + `EMAIL_TO` (or legacy `EMAIL_*` SMTP)
- Optional: `UPSTASH_*`, Turnstile keys

Security: **`17-security.mdc`**
